1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Enzymes are nature's speedsters, speeding up reactions crucial for life.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:10,000
They lower the activation energy needed for chemical reactions, acting like keys to unlock processes.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Imagine a world without enzymes.

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:17,600
Metabolism would grind to a halt, and life as we know it would cease.

5
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:22,400
From digestion to DNA replication, enzymes power every reaction in your body.

6
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:28,400
These molecular machines are incredibly specific, ensuring the right reactions happen at the right time.

7
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:31,200
Curious about how enzymes shape our world?

